channel.title: Client 333 Help
channel.description:
simple question I think, what should I set each one of these to?
RS2 user client - release #333 Usage: node-id, port-offset, [lowmem/highmem], [free/members], storeid
I don't need help with anything else with 333, since I already stopped it from connecting to the web server, etc
(Working with Client 333 since that is were Jagex added prayer icons, skull icons, and the other icons above your head, since starting with Client 455 wasn't the greatest idea since im fairly new at working with clients)
